---
id: parameter-list-view
name: "Parameter List View"
description: ""
version: 1.0.0
parameters:
  - name: tools
    type: json
    description: "List of tools with name and description"
    required: true
    default:
    - name: edit_file
      description: "Edit an existing file by replacing a specific string with new content"
      parameters:
        - name: file_path
          type: string
          description: "Path to the file to edit"
          required: true
        - name: old_string
          type: string
          description: "The exact string to find and replace"
          required: true
        - name: new_string
          type: string
          description: "The replacement string"
          required: true
    - name: write_file
      description: "Create or overwrite a file with the given content"
      parameters:
        - name: file_path
          type: string
          description: "Path to the file to create or overwrite"
          required: true
        - name: content
          type: string
          description: "The full file content to write"
          required: true
    - name: get_document_errors
      description: "Get validation errors and warnings for the current document"
      parameters: []
  - name: schema
    type: json
    description: "Tool call schema defining the XML format for tool invocations"
    required: false
    default: >-
      {"call": "<tool_call><tool>[[tool]]</tool><params>[[params]]</params></tool_call>"}
---
## Tool Call Instructions

When you need to perform an action, use the following XML format to invoke a tool:

{% set schema_obj = schema %}
{% for tool in tools %}

### {{ tool.name }}

{{ tool.description }}

{% if tool.parameters and tool.parameters | length > 0 %} **Parameters:**
{% for param in tool.parameters %}

- `{{ param.name }}` ({{ param.type }}{% if param.required %}, required{% endif %}): {{ param.description }}

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% raw %}```{% endraw %}xml 

{{ schema_obj.call | replace("[[tool]]", tool.name) | replace("[[params]]", "...") }}

{% raw %}```{% endraw %}

{% endfor %}